scene.message:
Student: Lucky~!{wait_fr:32} Now I don't{nl}
have to go to cram school!{waitkey}Ah, but I can't go home{nl}
either, huh...{waitkey}If there were an exit with no{nl}
guard, I could slip outside~{waitkey}{ret}

Student: That idiot doesn't{nl}
grasp the gravity of the{nl}
situation at all!{waitkey}Forget taking entrance exams{nl}
— our lives might just end{nl}
right here!{waitkey}{ret}
